title: Anne McElvoy reviews the political week at Westminster
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device Anne McElvoy reviews the political week at Westminster 16 October 2015 Last updated at 11:31 BST
This Week sent its future technology correspondent Anne McElvoy - also from the Economist - to a 3D printing retailer for a multi-dimensional roundup of the political week.
She looks back on the headlines, where a vote on the economy dominated - and she looked for a model politician.
